data.description: Welcome to your charming sanctuary situated on a large .69 acre lot, and NO HOA! This adorable all brick 2 Bedroom, 2 Full bath home features a versatile bonus room that could easily serve as a 3rd bedroom! Beautiful hardwood floors in living room, hallway and 2 of the bedrooms, and tile in the bathrooms. The bathrooms have updated vanities and lighting. Spacious eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops, a breakfast bar, and all appliances stay. Just off the kitchen there is a cozy screened in porch, offering a bug free place to relax and enjoy the outdoors. The back porch leads to a huge backyard, perfect for kids, pets and entertaining! With plenty of room to grow and customize, this generous property provides endless possibilities for creating your dream oasis or adding to the existing living space! Prime location! less than a 5 minute drive to USC-Aiken, Aiken Regional Hospital, YMCA, and downtown Aiken. Easy access to Bridgestone, Fort Gordon and SRS! Qualifies for 100% USDA financing!
